description: How the Warriors won their second NBA championship in three years with a playoff run for the ages.
description_the_playoffs: The Warriors encountered little resistance en route to their third straight NBA Finals
description_the_parade: Blue skies, sunshine and an estimated 1 million fans greeted the Warriors as they celebrated their NBA championship

description_the_fans: This season brought Dance Mom and Toaster Guy -- who will become Golden State’s next viral sensation?
